{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2936e42b2","title":"给达赖喇嘛的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d46e41e808","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"b2936e42b2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"3f9dad4f41","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖喇嘛，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、西藏自治区筹备委员会主任委员。"},{"id":"c7fde5a734","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"阿沛·阿旺晋美，当时任西藏自治区筹备委员会秘书长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"79f602b8c6","type":"title","text":"给达赖喇嘛的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"3f9dad4f41","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的达赖喇嘛：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"c7fde5a734","type":"paragraph","text":"你托阿沛·阿旺普美?带给我的信收到了。我很高兴。阿沛我也见到了，并且由周总理和他谈了话。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"d991672c98","type":"paragraph","text":"西藏自治区筹备委员会在你领导下工作是做得好的，有成绩的。去年对实行民主改革提得早了，工作机构也太天了，这是缺点。现在决定在第二个五年计划期内不改革，并且把过大的机构作了精简，这就改正了缺点","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"aa70e86605","type":"paragraph","text":"工作中发生缺点总是难以完全避免的。对缺点，我们的态度应该是正确分析，积极改正，记取经验，继续前进。我们改掉了缺点以后，工作就会做得更好一些。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"016ca80958","type":"paragraph","text":"你在访问印度期间，拒绝了那些逃亡国外的反动分子出的环主意，是做得很对的。他们大概还要找机会进行反动活动，要教育僧俗官员对他们保持警惕。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"7e91709cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"西藏地方政府和堪厅间的关系问题，希望都能从团结愿望出发，双方好好协商加以解决很帖念你，希望你多注意健康，并多来信。祝你愉快！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"a0eab97060","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"},{"id":"c7e8081fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年八月十八日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2"}],"page":{"id":"99fc1dd5bd","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2936e42b2","start":208,"end":209}}}},"__N_SSG":true}